---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Secura • Stark Zero-Knowledge Suite">
  <div class="min-h-screen bg-[#050507] text-neutral-200 selection:bg-cyan-500 selection:text-black flex flex-col justify-between">
    <Header />
    
    <div class="flex-1 relative">
      <!-- Grid Background overlay -->
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(rgba(6,182,212,0.03)_1px,transparent_1px),linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(6,182,212,0.03)_1px,transparent_1px)] bg-[size:32px_32px] opacity-40 pointer-events-none"></div>
      <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/4 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-cyan-500/5 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-1/4 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-indigo-500/5 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>

      <!-- Content Container -->
      <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 sm:py-24 z-10">
        
        <!-- Header back button -->
        <div class="mb-12">
          <a 
            href="/" 
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-mono text-cyan-400 hover:text-cyan-300 transition-colors uppercase tracking-wider group"
          >
            <span class="transform group-hover:-translate-x-1 transition-transform inline-block">&larr;</span>
            <span>Back to Home</span>
          </a>
        </div>

      <!-- Hero Header -->
      <div class="border-b border-neutral-900 pb-10 mb-12">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-cyan-950/40 border border-cyan-500/30 text-[10px] font-mono font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-cyan-400 mb-6 shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(6,182,212,0.1)]">
          <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-cyan-400"></span>
          <span>ABOUT US</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-black tracking-tight text-white mb-6 font-mono">
          THE DUET OF <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-400 to-indigo-500 bg-clip-text text-transparent">SECURITY</span> AND PRODUCTIVITY.
        </h1>
        <p class="text-base text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
          Secura was founded with a singular, uncompromised mandate: to eliminate the friction between airtight, military-grade client security and raw professional productivity.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Grid Content -->
      <div class="grid gap-12 text-sm text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed font-sans">
        
        <!-- Section 1 -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white font-mono mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-cyan-400">//</span> 01. WHO WE ARE
          </h2>
          <p class="mb-4">
            We are a team of cryptographers, security architects, and product designers dedicated to crafting digital workspaces that respect the sovereignty of personal data. Tired of fragmented SaaS offerings that trade privacy for utility, we developed Secura (originally known as LifeHub AI) — a unified workspace suite that lets users manage mission-critical credentials, budget milestones, and invoicing in complete cryptographic isolation.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Section 2 -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white font-mono mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-cyan-400">//</span> 02. OUR ZERO-KNOWLEDGE PROMISE
          </h2>
          <p class="mb-4">
            In standard cloud platforms, your files, passwords, and accounting records are visible to server operators, administrators, and automated indexing engines. At Secura, we believe that access keys should be yours alone.
          </p>
          <p class="mb-4">
            By implementing client-side AES-GCM local cryptography, all passwords, bills, and transactional details are encrypted in your browser cache before they are securely synced. Your master key never leaves your machine, ensuring that not even our engineers can view or access your private records.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Section 3 -->
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white font-mono mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-cyan-400">//</span> 03. THE UNIFIED LANDSCAPE
          </h2>
          <p class="mb-4">
            Secura features five state-of-the-art developer and freelance-centric spaces integrated under a single, seamless console:
          </p>
          <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mt-6">
            <li class="bg-[#0b0b0f] border border-neutral-900 rounded-xl p-4">
              <strong class="text-white block font-mono text-xs mb-1 uppercase tracking-wider text-cyan-400">01. Password Vault</strong>
              Secure AES-GCM login encryption ensuring completely closed authentication archives.
            </li>
            <li class="bg-[#0b0b0f] border border-neutral-900 rounded-xl p-4">
              <strong class="text-white block font-mono text-xs mb-1 uppercase tracking-wider text-cyan-400">02. Freelance Invoices</strong>
              Dynamic, clean PDF creator for fast client billing and tax calculations.
            </li>
            <li class="bg-[#0b0b0f] border border-neutral-900 rounded-xl p-4">
              <strong class="text-white block font-mono text-xs mb-1 uppercase tracking-wider text-cyan-400">03. Expense Tracker</strong>
              Seamless logging of modern developer tool subscriptions and operational receipts.
            </li>
            <li class="bg-[#0b0b0f] border border-neutral-900 rounded-xl p-4">
              <strong class="text-white block font-mono text-xs mb-1 uppercase tracking-wider text-cyan-400">04. Expiry Countdown</strong>
              High-visibility live alert thresholds for key security credentials and domains.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

      </div>

      <!-- Footer stamp -->
      <div class="border-t border-neutral-900 mt-16 pt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4">
        <span class="text-[10px] font-mono text-neutral-600">SECURA SYSTEM INTEGRATION &bull; CORE v1.0.4</span>
        <a 
          href="/register" 
          class="h-9 px-6 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-500 to-indigo-600 text-white font-semibold text-xs flex items-center justify-center hover:opacity-95 transition-all shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(6,182,212,0.2)]"
        >
          Get Started For Free
        </a>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
    
  <Footer />
</div>
</Layout>
